quran[11{c,v,t}:
17,28,"agar unn se ( yani haajat mand rishta daaron, miskeeno aur musafiron se ) tumhe katrana ho, is bana par ke abhi tum Allah ki uss rehmat ko jis ke tum umeed waar ho talaash kar rahay ho, to inhen naram jawab day do"
17,29,nah to apna haath gardan se bandh rakho aur nah usay bilkul hi khula chore do ke malamat zada aur aajiz ban kar reh jao
17,30,teer a rab jis ke liye chahta hai rizaq kushadah karta hai aur jis ke liye chahta hai tang kar deta hai woh apne bundon ke haal se bakhabar hai aur inhen dekh raha hai
17,31,apni aulaad ko iflaas ke andaishay se qatal nah karo hum inhen bhi rizaq den ge aur tumhe bhi Dur haqeeqat unn ka qatal aik barri khata hai
17,32,zina ke qareeb nah phutkowoh bohat bura feal hai aur bara hi bura rasta
17,33,"qatal nafs ka irtikaab nah karo jisay Allah ne haraam kya hai magar haq ke sath aur jo shakhs mzlomanh qatal kya gaya ho is ke walii ko hum ne qisaas ke mutalbe ka haq ataa kya hai, pas chahiye ke woh qatal mein hadd se nah guzray, uss ki madad ki jaye gi"
17,34,"ma l- yateem ke paas nah phutko magar Ahsen tareeqay se, yahan taq ke woh apne shabab ko poanch jaye ehad ki pabandi karo, be shak ehad ke baray mein tum ko jawab dahi karni hogi"
17,35,"pemanay se do to poora bhar kar do, aur tolo to theek traazo se tolo yeh acha tareeqa hai aur bilhaaz injaam bhi yahi behtar hai"
17,36,"kisi aisi cheez ke peechay nah lagu jis ka tumhe ilm nah ho yaqeenan aankhh, kaan aur dil sab hi ki baz purse honi hai"
17,37,"zameen mein akarr kar nah chalo, tum nah zameen ko phaar satke ho, nah pahoron ki bulandi ko poanch satke ho"
17,38,inn umoor mein se har aik ka bura pehlu tairay rab ke nazdeek napasandeedah hai
